
force build-compose-shader
  mount shader-a, field shader
  mount shader-b, field shader
  mount mode, field xfermode

  cause invoke-constructor
    drive constructor, |ComposeShader|
    drive factor, share shader-a
    drive factor, share shader-b
    drive factor, share mode
    raise build, field compose-shader

